                <head>No. 112.<lb/>
                    <hi rend="italic">Mr. <persName type="from">Lowell</persName> to Mr. <persName
                            type="to">Frelinghuysen</persName>
                    </hi>.</head>
                <opener>
                    <seg rendition="#center">[Telegram.]</seg>
                </opener>
                <opener>
                    <dateline rendition="#right">
                        <placeName>
                            <hi rend="smallcaps">Legation of the United States</hi>,<lb/>
                            <hi rend="italic">London</hi>
                        </placeName>, <date calendar="gregorian" when="1882-03-07">
                            <hi rend="italic">March</hi> 7, 1882</date>.</dateline>
                </opener>
                <p>[Mr. Lowell reports that the instructions in Mr. Frelinghuysen’s dispatch of
                    March 4, 1882, have been obeyed, and that Earl Granville has informed him that
                    the matter will have immediate attention.]</p>
            </div>
        </body>
